fields.title: No, money down!
fields.dialog: [["Hutz", "Bart"], [0, "All right, Gentlemen, I'll take your case. But I'm going to have to ask for a thousand dollar retainer."], [1, "A thousand dollars? But your ad says \"No money down\"."], [0,"Oh! They got this all screwed up..."], [1,"So you don't work on a contingency basis?"], [0,"No, money down! Oops, I shouldn't have this Bar Association logo here either."]]
